      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-KJL0064-DELETE-RTN.

      *@원장을삭제하기전에테이블LOCK
           EXEC SQL
               LOCK TABLE DB2DBA.THKJL0064 IN EXCLUSIVE MODE
           END-EXEC

      *@원장삭제
           EXEC SQL
             DELETE  FROM  DB2DBA.THKJL0064
              WHERE 그룹회사코드   = :WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
                AND 기준년월일     = :WK-H-I-BASE-YMD
                AND "SUB한도구분"  = '4'
           END-EXEC

      *@삭제결과확인
