      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  SUB-LIMIT집계－유가증권매입약정－명목액기준(THKJL0064)등록
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3400-KJL0064-INSERT-RTN.

      *    초기화
           INITIALIZE TKJL0064-KEY
                      TRJL0064-REC

      *    그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  RJL0064-GROUP-CO-CD

      *    기준년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-YMD
             TO  RJL0064-BASE-YMD

      *    SUB한도구분＝＇4＇（유가증권매입약정－명목액기준）
           MOVE  CO-CHA-4
             TO  RJL0064-SUB-LIMT-DSTCD

      *    SUB한도（명목액기준）
           MOVE  WK-SUB-CLAM
             TO  RJL0064-SUB-CLAM

      *    SUB잔액（명목액기준）
           MOVE  WK-SUB-BAL
             TO  RJL0064-SUB-BAL

      *    DBIO CALL
           #DYDBIO INSERT-CMD-Y TKJL0064-PK TRJL0064-REC

      *    결과확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBIO-OK
                    ADD CO-NUM-1 TO WK-AC-INSERT-CNT
